I don't think you get my point, or maybe I did not get the point. Anyway, let's go with an example,

The original map {"CSTypeA":"foo", "CSTypeB":"bar"}
User try to update with map {"CSTypeC":"foo", "CSTypeD":"bar"}
I assume the expect result for the custmize state is {"CSTypeC":"foo", "CSTypeD":"bar"}.
But really by the default merge method we get: {"CSTypeA":"foo", "CSTypeB":"bar", "CSTypeC":"foo", "CSTypeD":"bar"}
CSTypeA and CSTypeB is the stale state that I meant.

